## 2026-03-27 - Arrow left/right don't expand/collapse groups
- Added ArrowLeft/ArrowRight keyboard handling for tree navigation in `handleListKeyDown`:
  - ArrowRight on collapsed group: expands it. On expanded group: moves focus to first child.
  - ArrowLeft on expanded group: collapses it. On collapsed group: moves focus to parent group.

